Package org.github.fussel178.telestion.extension.corfu.generator.template

Interface TemplateProvider

All Known Implementing Classes:
ResourceTemplateProvider
public interface TemplateProvider
A template provider resolves and loads the template files for the JinjaTemplateEngine and serves the template upon request.
